title: [P3D/FSX] Aerosoft - Split X v1.10
description:
Your chance to fly to the "Capital of Dalmatia", the biggest city of southern Croatia! Split lies on the Croatian Adriatic coast and is located on a peninsular making the approach towards the airport scenery a pure enjoyment. Photo realistic HD textures, perfectly modeled buildings and objects of the airport give you a great sense of the atmosphere of this area.
